UID:10010658-1772965800-1772978400@njaudubon.org
SUMMARY:Fin’s Sunday Social for NJ Audubon
DESCRIPTION:Fins Sunday Social to Support NJ Audubon | March 8th 10:30am-2:00pm \nWe are so grateful to Fins Bar & Grille for their generous support of NJ Audubon. Come out to Fins between 10:30am and 2:00pm on March 8th to enjoy some delicious food and drinks. Half of what you spend will be donated to the Cape May Bird Observatory and the Nature Center of Cape May. There will be live entertainment! Can’t wait to see you there. \nWHEN: Sunday\, March 8th\, 10:30am-2:00pm \nWHERE: Fins Bar & Grille (142 Decatur St\, Cape May\, NJ 08204) \n \n \n \n  \n 
URL:https://njaudubon.org/event/fins-sunday-social-for-nj-audubon-2/
LOCATION:NJ\, United States
CATEGORIES:Cape May Bird Observatory,Cape May Bird Observatory's Northwood Center,Event,Nature Center of Cape May
