SUMMARY:Nature Infused Cocktail Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an adults only program focused on infusing nature into your favorite adult beverages. We’ll be using some locally sourced native plants and popular craft cocktail embellishments. Each participant will craft two take-home infusions to pair with their favorite spirits and to share with friends and family! Please note\, alcohol is not provided at this workshop. \nThis is an indoor/outdoor event. Please dress appropriately for the weather as we will spend part of the evening touring and foraging plants outdoors. \nCOST: $35 Members\, $40 Non-members \nIMPORTANT INFORMATION: This is an indoor/outdoor event. Please dress appropriately for the weather as we will spend part of the evening touring and foraging plants outdoors. \nCANCELLATION: NJ Audubon’s programs require a minimum number of registrants to run. If we cancel\, due to lack of participation\, severe weather\, or unforeseen circumstances\, all participants will be notified as soon as possible and are eligible for a full refund. Participants may cancel without penalty if greater than 48 hours in advance. Sorry\, no refund for cancellations less than 48 hours in advance unless due to health emergencies; however\, registrations can be transferred to another program in the future. \nREGISTER HERE
